---
import BaseHead from '../components/BaseHead.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
import { SITE_TITLE } from '../consts';
---

<BaseHead title={`Product Solutions - ${SITE_TITLE}`} description="We specialize in certified secure hardware and communication solutions for enterprise and government requirements." />

<Header />
<main>
	<section class="hero">
		<div class="container">
			<h1>Product Solutions</h1>
			<p class="tagline">Certified Security Hardware & Communications</p>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section class="products-content">
		<div class="container">
			<div class="intro">
				<p>We specialize in identifying and providing certified security products that meet stringent government and enterprise requirements. Our focus is on solutions that align with international standards and New Zealand security frameworks.</p>
			</div>

			<div class="product-categories">
				<div class="category">
					<h2>Encrypted Storage Solutions</h2>
					<p>Hardware-encrypted storage devices that protect data at rest with certified encryption standards.</p>
					<ul>
						<li>FIPS 140-2 validated encryption</li>
						<li>Hardware-based AES-256 bit encryption</li>
						<li>PIN-authenticated access controls</li>
						<li>Cross-platform compatibility</li>
					</ul>
					<div class="status-note">
						<strong>Product Evaluation Phase:</strong> We are currently evaluating certified encrypted USB and storage solutions for our portfolio.
					</div>
				</div>

				<div class="category">
					<h2>Secure Communication Devices</h2>
					<p>Certified encrypted communication platforms for enterprise and specialized environments.</p>
					<ul>
						<li>End-to-end encrypted messaging</li>
						<li>Secure voice and video communication</li>
						<li>Commercial-grade encryption solutions</li>
						<li>Compliance with data protection standards</li>
					</ul>
					<div class="status-note">
						<strong>Market Research:</strong> Researching certified communication solutions that meet our security standards.
					</div>
				</div>

				<div class="category">
					<h2>Access Control & Authentication</h2>
					<p>Multi-factor authentication and secure access solutions for sensitive environments.</p>
					<ul>
						<li>Hardware security tokens</li>
						<li>Multi-factor authentication devices</li>
						<li>Biometric authentication solutions</li>
						<li>Physical access control systems</li>
					</ul>
					<div class="status-note">
						<strong>Vendor Selection:</strong> Assessing authentication solutions for enterprise deployment.
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>

			<div class="partner-cta">
				<h2>For Product Manufacturers & Distributors</h2>
				<p>Are you a manufacturer of certified security products? We are seeking partnership opportunities with companies offering:</p>
				<ul>
					<li>FIPS 140-2 certified encryption products</li>
					<li>NLNCSA DEP-V & NATO Restricted certified solutions</li>
					<li>NZISM-aligned security hardware</li>
					<li>Enterprise-grade secure communication devices</li>
				</ul>
				<p>We are building our product portfolio and welcome discussions with qualified manufacturers and distributors.</p>
				<a href="mailto:hello@hermetrix.nz?subject=Product Partnership Inquiry" class="btn primary">Discuss Partnership</a>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>
</main>
<Footer />

<style>
	.hero {
		padding: 3rem 1rem;
		text-align: center;
		background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f8fafc 0%, #e2e8f0 100%);
	}

	.hero h1 {
		font-size: 2.5rem;
		margin-bottom: 1rem;
		color: #1a365d;
	}

	.tagline {
		font-size: 1.25rem;
		color: #4a5568;
		max-width: 600px;
		margin: 0 auto;
	}

	.products-content {
		padding: 4rem 1rem;
		background: white;
	}

	.intro {
		text-align: center;
		max-width: 800px;
		margin: 0 auto 3rem;
		font-size: 1.1rem;
		line-height: 1.7;
	}

	.product-categories {
		max-width: 800px;
		margin: 0 auto 4rem;
	}

	.category {
		background: #f8fafc;
		padding: 2rem;
		margin-bottom: 2rem;
		border-radius: 0.5rem;
		border-left: 4px solid #1a365d;
	}

	.category h2 {
		color: #1a365d;
		margin-bottom: 1rem;
		font-size: 1.3rem;
	}

	.category ul {
		margin: 1rem 0;
		padding-left: 1.5rem;
	}

	.category li {
		margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
		line-height: 1.6;
	}

	.status-note {
		background: #e6fffa;
		border: 1px solid #81e6d9;
		border-left: 4px solid #38b2ac;
		padding: 1rem;
		border-radius: 0.25rem;
		margin-top: 1.5rem;
		font-size: 0.9rem;
	}

	.partner-cta {
		background: #1a365d;
		color: white;
		padding: 3rem;
		border-radius: 0.5rem;
		max-width: 800px;
		margin: 0 auto;
		text-align: center;
	}

	.partner-cta h2 {
		margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
		color: #90cdf4;
	}

	.partner-cta ul {
		text-align: left;
		max-width: 600px;
		margin: 1.5rem auto;
	}

	.partner-cta li {
		margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
		line-height: 1.6;
	}

	.btn {
		display: inline-block;
		padding: 0.75rem 2rem;
		margin-top: 1rem;
		text-decoration: none;
		border-radius: 0.375rem;
		font-weight: 600;
		transition: all 0.2s;
		background-color: #90cdf4;
		color: #1a365d;
	}

	.btn:hover {
		background-color: #63b3ed;
	}

	.container {
		max-width: 1200px;
		margin: 0 auto;
	}
</style>
